| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 0 | — |
| 🟡 Moderate | 5 | Triple-regex chain in `Underscore` (4 allocs/call × millions) |
| ℹ️ Info | 2 | Redundant regex eval, unsealed class |

